J Safra Asset Management Corp: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback




























j safra asset management corp
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Asset Management
Sub-Industry: Wealth Management
J.Safra Asset Management Corp provides investment advisory services. The Company offers financial planning, portfolio management, consulting, investment supervisory, and account consolidation services. J.Safra Asset Management serves its clients in the United States.




Corporate Information
Address:

550 5th Avenue
New York, NY 10036
United States


