            Business Description
        



J. Safra Asset Management Corporation, which also operates under the name Safra Asset Management, is located in New York, New York. This organization primarily operates in the Investment Advisory Service business / industry within the Security & Commodity Brokers, Dealers, Exchanges & Services sector. This organization has been operating for approximately 29 years. J. Safra Asset Management Corporation is estimated to generate $7.7 million in annual revenues, and employs approximately 30 people at this headquarters location.









Sector:

Security & Commodity Brokers, Dealers, Exchanges & Services



