Questions & Answers









What are the annual sales for J. Safra Asset Management Corporation?





J. Safra Asset Management Corporation generates approximately $7.7 million in annual sales.







Who is the Chairman of J. Safra Asset Management Corporation?





The Chairman of J. Safra Asset Management Corporation is Nicholas Berggruen.







How long has J. Safra Asset Management Corporation been in business?





J. Safra Asset Management Corporation has been in business for approximately 29 years.









Is there a key contact at J. Safra Asset Management Corporation?





Nicholas Berggruen is the Chairman of the Board at J. Safra Asset Management Corporation. You can contact Nicholas at (212) 704-5553.







How many people work at J. Safra Asset Management Corporation?





J. Safra Asset Management Corporation has approximately 30 employees at this location.







How big is J. Safra Asset Management Corporation?





J. Safra Asset Management Corporation is estimated to generate $7.7 million in annual revenues, and employs approximately 30 people. They occupy this facility which is approximately 11,000 square feet.







What is the phone number for J. Safra Asset Management Corporation?





The phone number for J. Safra Asset Management Corporation is (212) 704-5553







What is the internet address for J. Safra Asset Management Corporation?





The website (URL) for J. Safra Asset Management Corporation is www.safra.com.







